title: ‘Kirby Jenner’ Is the Best Thing on Quibi
description:
Is Quibi actually good? Kate Halliwell is joined by Danny Heifetz to explain why he loves the streaming service and tell you about his favorite Quibi shows, including ‘Reno 911!’ and ‘Kirby Jenner.’

Hosts: Kate Halliwell and Danny Heifetz
